{
  "texts": [
    "The findings show that the accuracy for RF, ETC, and XGBoost is 81.65%, 83.10%, and 83.52%, respectively.",
    "The findings are consistent with the prediction that using the KNN imputer to fill in the missing values will enhance the outcomes since machine learning models perform better with the missing values dataset than without.",
    "The suggested VC (XGB+RF +ETC) ensemble model has the greatest accuracy rate of any model, at 99.41%.",
    "A precision value of 97.63%, a recall value of 95.96%, and an F1 score of 96.76% are also shown for the suggested ensemble model.",
    "The accuracy value for the linear model LR, on the other hand, is the lowest at 73.57%."
  ]
}